abstract: Western Kentucky beats University of South Florida, 45-35, in Miami Beach Bowl; other college football news noted.
lead_paragraph: Brandon Doughty capped his career by throwing for 461 yards and three touchdowns as No. 25 Western Kentucky beat South Florida, 45-35, in the Miami Beach Bowl.
